<item>
            <title>[LU-17637] sanity test_56xk: &apos;lfs mirror resync -W&apos; too slow in VM</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17637</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for S Buisson &amp;lt;sbuisson@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/0f36091a-6dc4-4dc0-b309-dcc2e0919db1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/0f36091a-6dc4-4dc0-b309-dcc2e0919db1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_56xk failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&apos;lfs mirror resync -W&apos; too slow in VM (51 &amp;gt; 3.5 * 5)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/18001&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/18001&lt;/a&gt; - 5.4.0-135-generic&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/18001&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/18001&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.27.1.el8_lustre.ddn17.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test output is weird, it says ignore error but the error is actually triggered:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;running in VM &apos;kvm&apos;, ignore error
 sanity test_56xk: @@@@@@ IGNORE (env=kvm): &apos;lfs mirror resync -W&apos; slow (51 &amp;gt; 1.2 * 5) 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;





&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_56xk - &apos;lfs mirror resync -W&apos; too slow in VM (51 &amp;gt; 3.5 * 5)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
